</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/075d661417b8ca5a991a2a7bd4991cc1ab856d9d" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.671ex; width:2.411ex; height:2.509ex;" alt="{\displaystyle B,}"></span> the measure of <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle A}">
