  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/5c3461c1d8af1b996d6d65f574058e2ad25fd5d3" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:9.927ex; height:2.843ex;" alt="{\displaystyle \mu (\varnothing )=0.}"></span></li>
<li><b>Countable additivity</b> (or <a href="/wiki/Sigma_additivity" class="mw-redirect" title="Sigma additivity"><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle \sigma }">
  <semantics>
