<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Measure_of_countable_unions_and_intersections">Measure of countable unions and intersections</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Measure_(mathematics)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: Measure of countable unions and intersections"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="Countable_subadditivity">Countable subadditivity</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Measure_(mathematics)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: Countable subadditivity"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h4>
