<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="Continuity_from_below">Continuity from below</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Measure_(mathematics)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7" title="Edit section: Continuity from below"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h4>
<p>If <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle E_{1},E_{2},E_{3},\ldots }">
