</math></div><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/315aacc1120f320f550e90c27ce80700cf4b79d8" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-display mw-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -2.338ex; width:48.92ex; height:4.343ex;" alt="{\displaystyle \mu \{x\in X:f(x)\geq t\}=\lim _{t_{n}\uparrow t}\mu \{x\in X:f(x)&gt;t_{n}\}.}"></div>
The right-hand side <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle \lim _{t_{n}\uparrow t}F\left(t_{n}\right)}">
