</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/09299765be82f3d0548ad4b1e5f59bf9da6f48ca" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -2.338ex; width:9.612ex; height:4.343ex;" alt="{\displaystyle \lim _{t_{n}\uparrow t}F\left(t_{n}\right)}"></span> then equals <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle F(t)=\mu \{x\in X:f(x)&gt;t\}}">
