</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/5644459171f86de9b2d5d981c7f127a6a23d4dca" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.671ex; width:8.589ex; height:2.509ex;" alt="{\displaystyle s\in \mathbb {R} _{&gt;0}.}"></span> Then the <a href="/wiki/Packing_dimension#Definitions" title="Packing dimension">packing measure</a> <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle {\cal {H}}^{s}|{\cal {B}}}">
