<p>We say the <b>semifinite part</b> of <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle \mu }">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
