<ul><li><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle \mu =\{(\emptyset ,0)\}\cup ({\cal {A}}\setminus \{\emptyset \})\times \{+\infty \}.}">
