</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/52e7d0934a4f73b837248102850c848b8b774153" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.338ex; width:2.55ex; height:2.343ex;" alt="{\displaystyle {\cal {A}}.}"></span> In fact, among such measures <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle \xi ,}">
